text: Gjorgji Talevski (born 15 March 1976) is a former Macedonian professional basketball Power forward who played for clubs like MZT Aerodrom,http://basketball.eurobasket.com/player/Gjorgi_Talevski/FYR- Macedonia/KK_Pelister_Sport_Bitola/34850 and Pelister. ==External links== * * ==References== Category:1976 births Category:Macedonian men's basketball players Category:Living people Category:KK MZT Skopje players Category:Power forwards (basketball)
